* Queues and authorizations for the SPB app on localhost (dev)
* Generated by dev/ibmmq/gen-setup-spb-queues.sh from .env (IBMMQ_* variables).
* Channel DEV.APP.SVRCONN and user app already exist in the official IBM MQ Developer image.
*
* Convention: QL.{TYPE}.{SENDER}.{RECIPIENT}.NN = inbound; QR.* = outbound (application send).
*   QL.STG.NOTIFY.01 is only consumed by the StageServer; do not include it in queue_manager.queues in .env.
*